Sadie: “How can I help you?”

Player_ch: “I have trouble talking to the last citizen because he keeps running away.”

Sadie: “His name is Nate. He loved being around others and thrived on making people laugh. One day we all climbed the mountain and found a wonderful cave we wanted to explore. Nate tripped and got hurt, so we rushed out and accidentally left his favourite lamp behind. Ever since then, he's had trouble sleeping. We tried to get it back, but after we left, the cave door closed and locked itself with a difficult puzzle that none of us could solve. Now he's scared and anxious, which isn't the Nate we know.”

Player_ch: “I'll go up the hill and get his lamp.”

Player_ch: “Thank you!”